			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Of Gitnuganaks, Glaciers, and Life at the End of the Last Ice Age</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Off the British Columbia coast, scientists guided by Indigenous knowledge are unearthing evidence of island life long, long ago.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/devon-bidal/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Devon Bidal</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
